{
  "stem": "5357.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So when my sister said it, it's-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my father gathered the girls, because the boy, he-- my father knew he would not go on his own.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he said that Sarah and Naomi should go together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Me, he gave to the court reporter, because he also became our friend.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Ludwiczek was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my oldest, Rachel, that was oldest from the bunch that wasn't married yet, she went to this Karolek, to the sergeant.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we knew where everybody is going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, Sarah and Naomi were supposed-- they were supposed to go to the house, where we had our house, to the Polish people that we knew.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was supposed to go to this Ludwiczek.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my sister went to Karolek.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so my sister got a diamond ring, a beautiful diamond ring from my brother to give to this Karolek for keeping her.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, I got some merchandise from my sister's store.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so did the other two sisters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at night, we would-- as I said, there were no Germans standing near the-- near the fences, so we could go over the fences very easily.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And each one went to-- to where they were supposed to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My sister Rachel, she said, we're not going unless you go with us, to my father and mother and brother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said, I lived to do the commandments.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I did them already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But you girls did not have a chance, so you have to survive, just like it's written in the Torah, [SPEAKING HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you have to get married and have a family on your own.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we are only going to hamper you in your survival.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
